  <summary date="2019-08-23T12:37:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Help Separated Families Act of 2018

This bill helps reunify children of detained or deported parents with their parents, legal guardians, or relatives and expands requirements governing state plans for foster care and adoption assistance to include provisions that assist children separated from detained or deported parents.</summary>
